meta.@content: This file contains a pattern of three routes for a network: a primary, alternate and second-alternate (tertiary). By pushing the buttons, the packets move forward along their predetermined routes for one iteration. Routing and interpolators are pre-wired to move left-to-right only.
An experimental version of X3D JSON encoding is used for this scene.  Status online at http://www.web3d.org/wiki/index.php/X3D_JSON_Encoding
